rComments: Loved her teaching style, uses powerpoint for lectures and posts online. Always available to students. Amazing prof, would recommend taking the class. :)

Achvarina is very helpful and went to the extent to provide several handouts and sample questions before tests.  You can afford to skip a few lectures, but do not sleep on the readings.  If you incorporate readings into your essay answers in a thoughtful manner, she will mark generously.  Also, I found her very cute!
